snippet.title: [HINDI] BGIS 2024 | SEMI-FINALS 2 | Day 2 | BGMI
snippet.description:
Welcome to SEMI-FINALS 2 of the BGIS 2024! 

Prepare to be thrilled as 24 fierce teams from SEMI-FINALS 1 clash in the ultimate esports showdown. ONLY the top 8 teams will advance to the GRAND LAN FINALS in HYDERABAD 🔥

BATTLEGROUNDS MOBILE INDIA SERIES 2024. It's a battlefield where legends #makewaves. With a whopping prize pool of INR 2 Crores, stakes are higher than ever.

Stay tuned! Witness emerging stars rise to fame and write their names in the BGIS history. Who will dominate? Who will surprise? Join us at 3:30 PM from Thursday to Sunday.

Don't forget to like, subscribe, and hit the notification bell to keep up with all the action. Your favourite players need your cheers, so drop your support in the comments below!


#MAKEWAVES  #BATTLEGROUNDSMOBILEINDIA  #INDIAKAGAME

snippet.description:

#AuronMeinKahanDumTha Trailer Out Now! 

Starring Ajay Devgn, Tabu, Jimmy Shergill, Shantanu Maheshwari, and Saiee Manjrekar, and directed by Neeraj Pandey. Set to release on July 5, 2024.

snippet.title: Bhide की किस हरकत पर भड़का Jethalal? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | 13 June 2024
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Bhide is in huge trouble as the whistle gets stuck inside his throat. All advice from doctors and suggestions by friends seem to be of no use. Meanwhile, Bhide's unusual condition becomes the talk of the town and some start making fun of him. Will Bhide find a cure for his problem? 


Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 116
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Click Here To Watch More Episodes Of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G3i410QcyXWJgiYVDy6Vcw9

snippet.title: Mirzapur Season 3 - Official Teaser | Pankaj Tripathi, Ali Fazal, Shweta Tripathi, Rasika Dugal
snippet.description:
Jungle mein bhaukaal machne wala hai!🔥
#MirzapurOnPrime, July 5

About Prime Video: Prime Video is a premium streaming service that offers Prime members a collection of award-winning Amazon Original series, thousands of movies & TV shows—all with the ease of finding what they love to watch in one place. Prime Video is just one of the many benefits of a Prime membership, available for just ₹1499/ year. 
Included with Prime Video: Thousands of acclaimed TV shows & movies across languages & geographies, including Indian films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Shakuntala Devi, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, and HOME, along with Indian-produced Amazon Original series like Farzi, Jubilee, Dahaad, The Family Man, Mirzapur, Made in Heaven, Four More Shots Please!, Mumbai Diaries 26/11, Suzhal – The Vortex, Modern Love, Paatal Lok, Bandish Bandits, Guilty Minds, Cinema Marte Dum Tak, and Amazon Original movies like Maja Ma & Ammu. Also included are popular global Amazon Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Reacher, Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan, The Boys, Hunters, Fleabag, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel, & many more, available for unlimited streaming as part of a Prime membership. Prime Video includes content across Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi, & Bengali. 
Prime Video Mobile Edition: Consumers can also enjoy Prime Video’s exclusive content library with Prime Video Mobile Edition at ₹599 per year. This single-user, mobile-only annual video plan offers everyone access to high-quality entertainment exclusively on their mobile devices. Users can sign-up for this plan via the Prime Video app (on Android) or website. 
Instant Access: Prime Members can watch anywhere, anytime on the Prime Video app for smart TVs, mobile devices, Fire TV, Fire TV stick, Fire tablets, Apple TV, & multiple gaming devices. Prime Video is also available to consumers through Airtel and Vodafone pre-paid & post-paid subscription plans. In the Prime Video app, Prime members can download episodes on their mobile devices & tablets & watch anywhere offline at no additional cost.
Enhanced experiences: Make the most of every viewing with 4K Ultra HD- & High Dynamic Range (HDR)-compatible content. Go behind the scenes of your favourite movies & TV shows with exclusive X-Ray access, powered by IMDb. Save it for later with select mobile downloads for offline viewing. 
Video Entertainment Marketplace: In addition to a Prime Video subscription, customers can also purchase add-on subscriptions to other streaming services, as well as, get rental access to movies on Prime Video. Prime Video Channels: Prime Video Channels offers friction-free & convenient access to a wide range of premium content from multiple video streaming services all available at a single destination – Prime Video website & apps. Prime Members can buy add-on subscriptions & enjoy a hassle-free entertainment experience, simplified discovery, frictionless payments, & more. Rent: Consumers can enjoy even more movies from new releases to classic favourites, available to rent – no Prime membership required. View titles available by visiting primevideo.com/store. The rental destination can be accessed via the STORE tab on primevideo.com & the Prime Video app on Android smart phones, smart-TVs, connected STBs, & Fire TV stick.

#mirzapur #primevideoindia

snippet.title: Clean Sewers, Prevent Floods | Dimapur Monsoon | Dreamz Unlimited
snippet.description:
Improper disposal of waste clogs our drainage systems, leading to severe flooding, especially during the monsoon season. These floods not only disrupt daily life but also become breeding grounds for various diseases. Let's work together to prevent water logging and protect our communities from health hazards. 
Remember, a small change in our habits can make a big difference!

This video is an initiative of,
Dimapur Municipal Council

snippet.title: MEAT HUNT | MUTTON KARAHI | Pakistani Recipe Cooking In Indian Village | Mutton Street Food Recipe
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook a Pakistani special Peshawari Karahi recipe with 80kg of mutton meat. This mutton karahi recipe is one of the famous street food recipe in Pakistan. It looks like mutton curry, but we don't need to add masala or spices. Simply add tomato and chili after frying the mutton meat in the oil.

Finally, we enjoy the mutton curry recipe in the evening. The taste is delicious!

Episode 4110: Jethalal Feels Anxious
--------------------------------------------------------
Bagha and Bawri head to collect Jethalal’s cheque, leaving Jethalal anxious. They arrive at Mr. Daruwala’s resort. Will they succeed in collecting the cheque?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4110 | 13 June 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Goblin Queen's Takeover | Clash Royale Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Begin the Goblin Queen's Journey on June 17th!
Conquer new Arenas with the Goblin Queen and unlock new Goblin Cards to join her!

Stay tuned for more info!

Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashRoyale/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashroyale
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashroyale
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashRoyale/

ENTER THE ARENA
Build your Battle Deck and outsmart the enemy in fast real-time battles. From the creators of CLASH OF CLANS comes a real-time multiplayer battle game starring your favourite Clash characters and more. Start battling against players from around the world!

BECOME A MASTER OF STRATEGY AND DECK BUILDING
Choose unique Cards to your Battle Deck and head to the Arena for Battle!
Place your Cards right and knock down the enemy King and Princesses from their Towers in a strategic and fast-paced match.

COLLECT AND UPGRADE 100+ CARDS
Hog Rider! Collect and upgrade 100+ Cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defences you know and love and many others. Win battles and progress to new Arenas to unlock powerful new Cards to your collection!

BATTLE YOUR WAY TO THE TOP
Battle your way to the League and Global Tournaments to match against the best players in the world.
Compete for glory and rewards!

SEASONAL EVENTS
Unlock new Seasonal items like Tower Skins, Emotes and powerful Magic Items with the Season Pass and participate in fun Challenges that put your skills to the test!

JOIN A CLAN AND GO TO WAR
Join or form a Clan with other players to share Cards and battle in Clan Wars for BIG rewards!

See you in the Arena!
#ClashRoyale #goblinqueen #goblins

snippet.title: आधी रात में Daya लौट आई Gokuldham | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Jetha-Bhide Ki Nok Jhonk
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Jethalal went to a nice restaurant for dinner with his family but forgot his wallet at home. Now the restaurant manager won't let them leave till he has paid the bill. However, Bagha arrives at the nick of time and helps Jethalal out. Keep watching the episode to find out more.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 1849
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Jetha Aur Bhide Ki Nok Jhonk' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cTAUo34hpXVbh1keqAyhuhj

gusse mein pyaari laage,dil pai garari laage
chal ya tufani teri kachchee Farari laage

bijli tai jyaada laage roop ka jhataka

gusse mein pyaari laage,dil pai garari laage
chal ya tufani teri kachchee Farari laage

chaal banjaari teri re, hansi katari teri re

baat ye saari teri ra lairee supaari meri re
maar ke chodegee ke pooree sai taiyaari teri re

badaree sai garmee darami,cool bhee lagaaya kar  
tem sai kharaab kallee shahar na jaaya kar
chadhati jawani teri, theek na shaitani teri
naajuk se dil pai  painee see aaree laage
gusse mein pyaari laage,dil pai garari laage
chal ya tufani teri kachchee Farari laage

                                   (3)
jache sai dres res choraya me hod hori
raharee na chook luk maa ki su tod hori
piyush teri wait kare, aajya ne kyoo let kare
balambhiye ajamer gelaya sab pai too bhaari laage 
gusse mein pyaari laage,dil pai garari laage
chal ya tufani teri kachchee Farari laage

snippet.title: प्रहस्त, दुर्मुख और मकराक्ष का वध | रामायण | दिव्य कथाएँ
snippet.description:
भक्त को भगवान से और जिज्ञासु को ज्ञान से जोड़ने वाला एक अनोखा अनुभव। तिलक प्रस्तुत करते हैं दिव्य भूमि भारत के प्रसिद्ध धार्मिक स्थानों के अलौकिक दर्शन। दिव्य स्थलों की तीर्थ यात्रा और संपूर्ण भागवत दर्शन का आनंद। दर्शन दो भगवान! 

Watch the video song of ''Darshan Do Bhagwaan'' here - https://youtu.be/j7EQePGkak0

सेनानायक वज्रमुष्टि के मारे जाने के पश्चात रावण का द्वितीय पुत्र प्रहस्त युद्ध भूमि में आकर वानर सेना को नष्ट करने लगता है, जिसे रोकने के लिए लक्ष्मण को स्वयं युद्ध लड़ने आते है और प्रहस्त के मायावी अस्त्रों के वार को विफल करते हुए उसका वध कर देते है और दूसरी तरफ हनुमान असुर दुर्मुख का अपने घुटने से गला दबा कर वध कर देते है। दुर्मुख और प्रहस्त के मारे जाने के पश्चात खर का पुत्र और रावण का भतीजा मकराक्ष अपने पिता खर की हत्या का प्रतिशोध लेने युद्ध क्षेत्र में आता है और सुग्रीव के युद्ध के लिए आगे आने पर कहता है कि उसका युद्ध केवल राम से ही होगा क्योंकि वह राम का मस्तक ले कर ही जाएगा। लक्ष्मण द्वारा मकराक्ष का उपहास उड़ाने पर श्री राम उसे समझाते है कि किसी भी योद्धा की चुनौती का उपहास नहीं उड़ाना चाहिए। राम मकराक्ष की चुनौती स्वीकार करते हुए वचन देते हैं कि यदि इस युद्ध में वे मारे जाते हैं तो उनका कटा हुआ सिर मकराक्ष को सौंप दिया जाएगा ताकि वो अपनी माँ को दिया हुआ वचन पूरा कर सके। राम और मकराक्ष में युद्ध प्रारम्भ होता है, लेकिन मायावी मकराक्ष अपने अस्त्रों के प्रहारों के विफल रहने पर अपनी कई मायावी छवि बना लेता है। जब राम समझ नहीं पाते है कि असली मकराक्ष कौन है, तब विभीषण उन्हें समझाते है कि केवल असली मकराक्ष के घावों से रक्त बहेगा। बहते रक्त से असली मकराक्ष को पहचान कर श्री राम अपना बाण चलाकर उसका वध कर देते है।

संसार में मनुष्य को धर्म के अनुरुप मर्यादित जीवन जीने की शिक्षा देने के लिए युगों से विभिन्न कथाओं के माध्यम से शिक्षित करने का प्रयास किया गया है। सनातन धर्म में कथाओं को विशेष महत्व है और मनुष्य के जन्म से लेकर मृत्यु तक हर अवसर के लिए कथा, हर पूजा-विधान के लिए कथा। इन कथाओं को सुनने व अनुसरण करने से मानव के सामाजिक जीवन में विशेष प्रभाव पड़ता है और रामायण और भगवत् गीता जैसे महान ग्रंथो (कथाओं) में मानव जीवन का सार छुपा है। यह दिव्य कथाएं धार्मिक, सांस्कृतिक और मानवीय मूल्यों से परिचय करा मनुष्य को सामाजिक जीवन जीने के कला को निपुण बनाने का कार्य करने के साथ प्रेरणा का कार्य करती है। “तिलक” अपने इस नये संकलन “दिव्य कथाएं” में सर्वप्रथम रामायण से जुड़े प्रसंगों को आपके समक्ष प्रस्तुत करेगा। भक्ति भाव से इनका आनन्द लीजिये और तिलक से जुड़े रहिये।

#tilak #ramayan #kathayen #divyakathayen #ayodhya #ayodhyarammandir #rammandir

snippet.title: #Video | बघवा जिंदा बा | Arvind Akela Kallu | Prabha Raj | Sapna Chauhan | नया भोजपुरी गाना
snippet.description:
उठ गया शेर जंगल में, सारे सतर्क हो जाओ #ArvindAkelaKallu का गाना #BaghwaZindaBa सारे #bhojpuriindustry  में आग लगाने आ गया है |

Subscribe to our channel for more Bhojpuri Songs:  @SaregamaHumBhojpuri  

Credits:
Song Name: Baghwa Zinda Ba ( बघवा जिंदा बा )
Singer - Arvind Akela Kallu & Prabha Raj
Feat - Arvind Akela Kallu & Sapna Chauhan
Writter - Bhagirath Pathak
Music - Arya Sharma
Choreographer:- Lakkie Vishwakarma
DOP - Yogesh Singh
Editor - Anand Kumar(Santu)
Assistant Choreographer - Ashu & Suresh
DI - Rohit Singh
Production - Aakash Vishwakarma

Lyrics:

मुखड़ा=F मि लेना आई पापा भईया के डरे..... 
छापा पड़ल बा जानूहमरा घरे ....
M=। हमरा रहतेबोल रेपगली कवना बात के िचंता बा
तोरा के कवन हाथ लगा दी जबलेबघवा िजंदा बा ......
अंतरा M गमी जानतरेकहा अभी खून के.... 
हाथ मेलेके चलीला कानून के
F= एने लि लार पर रायफल तनल बा
लव मेए जानूखतरा बनल बा
M र ति भर ना फ रक पड़ेकरत कवन िनंदा बा
अंतरा=m कहबेत गउवा के गांव उड़वा देब
अईसन ना होई त मोछ मुड़वा देब
F.. कलूहो ओकर भागीरथ सेबा इयारी
जईब धाराई त जान सेदी मारी
M= जि ला भर मेपगला तोर गुणन मेचुिनंदा बा

Lyrics:

mukhda=F mile na aai papa bhaiya ke dare....
chhapa padal ba janu hamra ghare 
M= hamra rahte bol re pagli kawna bat ke chinta ba 
Tora ke kawan hath laga di jable baghwa jinda ba 
Antra=M Garmi jantare kaha abhi khun ke...
hath me leke chalila kanoon ke 
F=ene lilar par rayfal tanal ba 
Love me e Babu khatra banal ba....
M=rati bhar na fark pade karat kawan ninda ba 
Tora ke kawan hath lagadi jable baghwa jinda ba 
Antra=M kahbe ta gauwa ke gaw udwa Deb 
Aisan na hoi ta mochh mudwa Deb 
F=kallu ho okar Bhagirath se ba yari 
Jaib dharai ta jaan se di mari 
M=jila bhar me pagla tor gundan me chuninda ba 
Tora ke kawan hath laga di jable baghwa jinda b

#BaghwaZindaBa
#arvindakelakallu 
#saregamahumbhojpuri 
#newbhojpurisong 
#bhojpurisong 
#bhojpurigana

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Shiddat Episode 38 [Eng Sub] - Muneeb Butt - Anmol Baloch - 11th June 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Asra, a beautiful and cherished young woman, has led a life filled with love and care from her family. In contrast, Sultan, a determined and charismatic perfectionist, overcomes the challenges of his troubled childhood to consistently achieve his desires.

Despite their stark personality differences, Asra falls in love with Sultan. However, after they marry, Asra realizes that Sultan is not the ideal man she had envisioned. To please him, she sacrifices her desires and undergoes a significant transformation.

This revelation becomes the catalyst for an unending series of problems between them. The journey through marital life becomes a complex maze as Asra and Sultan attempt to navigate challenges, each trying to mold the other according to their own will and preference.

Will Asra and Sultan change for each other, or will the growing list of problems between them persist? When Asra discovers the reality about Sultan, how will she react? Is Sultan contemplating leaving Asra? Can love overcome all obstacles, or are some differences too profound to bridge?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
